Title: Good Evening, Mr. Wallenberg
Actors: Stellan Skarsgård, Katharina Thalbach, Károly Eperjes, Miklós B. Székely
Plot: Swedish national Raoul Wallenberg, newcomer to politics and international machinations, travels to German-occupied Budapest during WWII in order to effectively intervene in the fate of trapped Hungarian Jews, by providing them with safe passage to Sweden. Based on a true story.
